Nigerian rapper/actor, Falana Folarin, popularly known as Falz has debuted a new blonde look, leaving many tongues wagging. The star first deleted all his posts on Instagram in order to create space for it. However, the new look has elicited diverse reactions from his fans. Fellow musician, Simi commented and said, “Lol I’m so bothered.” Some others however, said they like the new look. See photos below: Source